{"id": "ChIJMZC_4EfGwoARcBndJpbF_nQ", "rating": 4.5, "userRatingCount": 1890, "displayName": {"text": "Entertainment Hobby Shop Jungle (Anime Jungle)", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Offbeat shop stocks a range of popular anime action figures, goods & collectibles in a simple space.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJMZC_4EfGwoARcBndJpbF_nQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4MlEyeEthV1ZOZUhCaFQyZEZMVTFrUkRKRE5rRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The staff is super friendly, helpful and knowledgeable! My fiancé has been coming here for years and has picked up good singles. I've been coming here with him for over a year.\n\nToday we got a box of the Battles of Legend Glorious Galary;  we pulled a Chibi card! 😆", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The staff is super friendly, helpful and knowledgeable! My fiancé has been coming here for years and has picked up good singles. I've been coming here with him for over a year.\n\nToday we got a box of the Battles of Legend Glorious Galary;  we pulled a Chibi card! 😆", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ashley Romero", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105677057864564962879/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-DuKTdtgc9ep3Qw4RqMKNy-hh3LXyTppkrXTLWoqZKpKsWsRVIg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-05T05:22:59.006743446Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4MlEyeEthV1ZOZUhCaFQyZEZMVTFrUkRKRE5rRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4MlEyeEthV1ZOZUhCaFQyZEZMVTFrUkRKRE5rRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c647e0bf9031:0x74fec59626dd1970"}, {"name": "places/ChIJMZC_4EfGwoARcBndJpbF_nQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWbVQzSktUM0k0V21aWVgyNTFaRlJvU2xZeFNHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "So many cute figurines and collectibles! Most of their stuff is pre-owned and marked down so you can get a really good deal on whatever you are looking for! The staff are very kind and attentive and will help you without hesitation. I got this super cute figurine. It’s poseable and has interchangable hand expressions and also an interchangeable face plate and moveable eyes! Very cute find in the Little Tokyo Mall. 🥰", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "So many cute figurines and collectibles! Most of their stuff is pre-owned and marked down so you can get a really good deal on whatever you are looking for! The staff are very kind and attentive and will help you without hesitation. I got this super cute figurine. It’s poseable and has interchangable hand expressions and also an interchangeable face plate and moveable eyes! Very cute find in the Little Tokyo Mall. 🥰", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "frogqueen slay", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117397772121813632027/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvuOR_MhJFf5an1D4izmABXr1EbjaEltGkujFXo2vOvDrOEd8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-28T04:09:14.623331612Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWbVQzSktUM0k0V21aWVgyNTFaRlJvU2xZeFNHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWbVQzSktUM0k0V21aWVgyNTFaRlJvU2xZeFNHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c647e0bf9031:0x74fec59626dd1970"}, {"name": "places/ChIJMZC_4EfGwoARcBndJpbF_nQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ZeVIyRmplV1YyV25kck56WkhRVjk2UkhrMVZFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I went to an Event for Godzilla, they were hosting it. It was an enjoyable experience, it was really fun for fans and collectors alike.\nPrices are fair, and they have a great selection of merchandise that I wanted to see that can't be found anywhere else.\nThe Staff is really nice and very professional and kept me informed about what recommendations very informative and im definitely coming back again in the future.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I went to an Event for Godzilla, they were hosting it. It was an enjoyable experience, it was really fun for fans and collectors alike.\nPrices are fair, and they have a great selection of merchandise that I wanted to see that can't be found anywhere else.\nThe Staff is really nice and very professional and kept me informed about what recommendations very informative and im definitely coming back again in the future.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Mathy", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108372833189324245228/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrYhM03GrP8Grn-CPcCefuaNFnC-2ehJuF9LumZ1OuturdJIk=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-06T06:43:24.821529260Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ZeVIyRmplV1YyV25kck56WkhRVjk2UkhrMVZFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ZeVIyRmplV1YyV25kck56WkhRVjk2UkhrMVZFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c647e0bf9031:0x74fec59626dd1970"}, {"name": "places/ChIJMZC_4EfGwoARcBndJpbF_nQ/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURuN2ZuYTRBRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "This little area in little Tokyo reminds me of Akihabara in the glory days before maid cafes took over. Alot of cool anime goods and world 8-2 retro video game store is there as well. You will need to be ready to spend though cos you will 110% see things you want. I spent a good 2 hrs exploring each shop.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This little area in little Tokyo reminds me of Akihabara in the glory days before maid cafes took over. Alot of cool anime goods and world 8-2 retro video game store is there as well. You will need to be ready to spend though cos you will 110% see things you want. I spent a good 2 hrs exploring each shop.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jason Bramble", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109495729681162618675/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ9zaiJblciaUrhEA9j9VXfWZSyHDveesq3MXx3u1_WD2VIKAs=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2024-10-08T19:52:18.548263Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURuN2ZuYTRBRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURuN2ZuYTRBRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c647e0bf9031:0x74fec59626dd1970"}, {"name": "places/ChIJMZC_4EfGwoARcBndJpbF_nQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaU1NYUXRaVkJuU1VOTVVtY3pWRFp0UzJwTFVFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Authentic, real unlike any shop anywhere. This stuff is so hard to come by and these guys stand behind everything. They have so many options and every worker truly loves what they do. I spoke with Rob and his service was beyond my expectations, professional, thorough and educative.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Authentic, real unlike any shop anywhere. This stuff is so hard to come by and these guys stand behind everything. They have so many options and every worker truly loves what they do. I spoke with Rob and his service was beyond my expectations, professional, thorough and educative.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Thadeus Young", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103712804576846894706/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJd1L_tf-oqhtazn00-h5sQiis-gMHT8vPtw3ZBuOf8P7FtSw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTim